<h1>What can MAC offer?</h1>
<ul>
<li>
<h2>Processing pipeline guarantees</h2>
<ul>
<li>Ensure that data is processed as required</li>
<li>Split processing into small, minimally trusted stages</li>
<li>Encryption, sanitization, virus scanning</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>
<h2>Authorization limits for legitimate users</h2>
<ul>
<li>Decompose administrator role</li>
<li>Partition users into classes based on position, clearance,
etc.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
